Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:24.06,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:29.35,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher教えて 未完成な僕ら
