Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.19,0:01:00.56,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}dropout mentality 凌駕於非日常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:05.30,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我們帶著一臉睡意
