Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:10.92,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}起立！敬禮！鎖定！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:15.82,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}曾經想著總有人會解決
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:21.38,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}多少帶著旁觀的心態
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:24.06,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:29.35,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher請告訴不成熟的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:34.85,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}何時才能擊倒你這個不落的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:40.35,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}只要挑戰 可能性是half＆half
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:45.34,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher請看著迷茫的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:50.59,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}為了你比任何人都認真學習
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:56.57,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}殺意就是唯一給你的信息
